Path: godot/classes/class_editorcommandpalette.rst
Summary: Property dialog_hide_on_ok and its override relationship with AcceptDialog

Property: dialog_hide_on_ok (bool): Controls whether the dialog is hidden after confirmation. Default: false. Note: This overrides the behavior defined in AcceptDialog's dialog_hide_on_ok property.
